{"tid":1531914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做唔到跳閘都可以幫忙抵制黨鐵!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-02T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T12:45:54.000Z","uid":243773,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"edd16ce76511477c7f3541e7a61a74dc37758981","tid":1531914,"uid":243773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"大家跳唔到閘唔緊要，但可以選擇唔好係港鐵站內消費。<br />\n<br />\n  根據港鐵 《2019中期業績報告》，港鐵每年有25億收入係車站零售設施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMMy4Ez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMMy4Ez.png&h=207e1076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  相信大家最常係港鐵站內 7-11或餅店買食物/飲品。好多時候出去遊行或者返工都見到大家係站內商店買水。希望大家可以行遠小小或者買定先。站內好多鋪頭都係加盟店。所以大家抵制佢地好難支持得住。<br />\n<br />\n  當站內鋪頭冇生意，租客就唔會再租。即使再租都會有空置期。大家做多一步黨鐵每年賺少十幾億，咁先會影響到港鐵班高層!!<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/interim2019/MTR_IR%202019_Chi_full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Farchive%2Fcorporate%2Fch%2Finvestor%2Finterim2019%2FMTR_IR%25202019_Chi_full.pdf&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR22Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ece992c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/interim2019/MTR_IR%202019_Chi_full.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，<br />\n時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d278f69dc840798d91d288a36b94b56ea42eda96","tid":1531914,"uid":71606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"同埋可以用長者八達通<br />\n對家嘅藍絲廢老優惠<br />\n<br />\n你唔用嘅話就係益咗佢哋"},{"pid":"18acfc38dd7850a03ede990e924296bb1c8df176","tid":1531914,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8be078e549f79f08293e016de9567d02fb8d6a","tid":1531914,"uid":249041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"真係盡量冇俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5339a3f617a4a6832442288bab5ede0efb328045","tid":1531914,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:19:52.000Z","msg":"推閘簡單好多，大力啲，亦都唔好喺地鐵站入面買野"},{"pid":"d0cd49f96cff71907b250e44bc655993db6a1153","tid":1531914,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"推，等佢無租收"},{"pid":"8aeeb8cf4b4ee364ffb8a95ceacd6a0c30825e75","tid":1531914,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c348bc8ce09e86f7398c0e6a625ac6cd5c405a30","tid":1531914,"uid":298763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f079dfe8ffb1cba1863df542e030cd06c7e68dea","tid":1531914,"uid":243773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"eed7d74c8520cf010ec8491c6075fc9660a28e14","tid":1531914,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"輕鐵撚表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20a70c2926eefe3dd72dfa26906dc7abfd8626a","tid":1531914,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg